<Layout title="generative design — sugiro.ai" description="A collection of generative design projects by Lula Rocha using Processing, JavaScript, Python, and Adobe Illustrator — creative programming and algorithmic art." footerColClass="col-span-12 desktop:col-start-7 desktop:col-span-2">
